data.description: Welcome to a charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house in a tranquil neighborhood with a spacious yard, brimming with potential. The exterior features a large, rear deck with ample space for entertaining and pets. Completely fenced and an established garden already in place. Inside, the living room features large windows and LVP floors. An open layout connects it to the dining room, creating versatile space. The kitchen is open to the dining and living room, with space for cooking and entertaining. The three bedrooms showcase ample space, with the master bedroom having an ensuite bathroom. The master bathroom has been completely updated with a walk in, tile shower. A unique feature is the powered workshop, a valuable space for DIY projects or hobbies. With a bit of vision and TLC, this house can be transformed into a dream home. The basement has a large, 2 car garage with a finished space that could be a 4th bedroom, office or in home gym. The house has newer roof, hvac and hot water heater.
